('55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555', 'The Strategic Retreat', 'In the heat of a comical chase, a rotund Batman is glancing back while sprinting awkwardly down a darkened street, his eyes wide in faux terror. The imposing figures of the bullies loom behind him, their shadows elongated and comically exaggerated. This dynamic scene is illustrated with heavy ink lines and deep blacks, emphasizing the humor and urgency in the style of Frank Miller.', 'https://fal.media/files/zebra/lVCWY8w4PELaVRgkuyZbx.png', 576, 1024, 'image/jpeg'),
('55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555', 'Batman vs. Bullies Showdown', 'The fake fat Batman stands defiantly against the three bullies, hands on his hips, portraying a mix of bravery and absurdity. His suit is too tight, accentuating his round belly, while the bullies, drawn with sharp, jagged edges in their features, are caught off guard. The background showcases a gritty urban environment filled with dark shadows that frame the action-packed moment, reminiscent of Frank Miller''s graphic novels.', 'https://fal.media/files/penguin/iEfnuJhwLU7NIfb-NOVsg.png', 576, 1024, 'image/jpeg'),
('55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555', 'The Great Escape Plan', 'A chubby Batman, breathing heavily, peers from behind a dumpster while the bullies search nearby. His eyes are wide with determination, and he holds a comedic gadget that looks overly complicated for his situation. The scene emphasizes the tension with dramatic shadows and intense lines typical of Frank Miller’s gritty comic aesthetic, creating a playful yet serious atmosphere.', 'https://fal.media/files/tiger/qxubZBGyl4RDNQV0sBCZd.png', 576, 1024, 'image/jpeg'),
